  "html": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\">Day 2 - Lesson 3</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">しらないひとが　だれか　きく = Asking someone about a person you don&#39;t know</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><b>ばしょ (Location):</b> パーティー = Party</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\"><b>とうじょうじんぶつ (Characters):</b> たかはしさん (Takahashi-san)、たなかさん (Tanaka-san)</span></p><div class=\"fr-view\"><p><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/bq84daehra84otn6ging\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D2  L3 C1.mp4 - 00:13\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p></div><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">The new words you find in this lesson are:</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">あの ひと (ano hito) = That person (over there)</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">ひと (hito) = person</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">だれ ですか (dare deska) = who is?</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">だれ (dare) = who</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">さとう さん (Satoo san) = Sato san</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\">すみません が (sumimasen) = I&#39;m sorry but...<br><br>しょうかい (shookai) = introduce</span></p>",
